com\/sri-lanka\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sri Lanka<\/a>. Escape the city with a 25-minute drive towards Kankesanthurai Beach. See the very clear blue waters and play around with the locals who are also chilling on the beach.<\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/6649&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155444\/things-to-do-jaffna-sri-lanka-pin.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155444\/things-to-do-jaffna-sri-lanka-pin-22x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155444\/things-to-do-jaffna-sri-lanka-pin-446x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"7 Great Things To Do in Jaffna, Sri Lanka\" height=\"600\" width=\"446\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>After the beach, head over the Keerimalai Pond which you can see as a natural swimming pool. A full tuk-tuk day-trip will cost you between 750 and 1500 LKR. You can also rent a motorbike in town and explore the coastlines on your own.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/travel\/colombo\/jaffna\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Get bus tickets from Colombo to Jaffna<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155535\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-beach.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"6650\" class=\"wp-image-6650 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155535\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-beach.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155535\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-beach-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155535\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-beach-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155535\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-beach-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155535\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-beach-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-c