n-food-24x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155512\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-indian-food.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Or when you are in for a fully local experience. Visit Malayan Cafe, near the market. This bakery-like Indian place serves all kinds of bread on a banana leaf. You will see 99% locals here and it&#x2019;s busy throughout the whole day.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>In for a dessert? A 5-min walk from Mangos is Rio Ice Cream. They have many kinds of flavors but be warned, this is not your Italian gelato. Sri Lankan people love their sweets. :)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155451\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-Malayan-Cafe.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"6675\" class=\"wp-image-6675 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155451\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-Malayan-Cafe.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155451\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-Malayan-Cafe-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155451\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-Malayan-Cafe-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018