a-Sri-lanka-dessert-1152x1440.jpg 1152w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155455\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-dessert-24x30.jpg\" src=\"\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155455\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-dessert.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"islands\">5. Visit one of the local Islands<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>One very popular thing to do in Jaffna is visiting one of the local islands. There are two popular islands. Nainativu Island can be visited by a short boat trip from the Kurikadduwan Jetty. Visit the temple or do an island tour.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155504\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-local-barber.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"6663\" class=\"wp-image-6663 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155504\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-local-barber.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155504\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-local-barber-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/04\/23155504\/Things-to-do-Jaffna-Sri-lanka-local-barber-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-con